{"tid":471211,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（公屋等於cheap?)長發邨公屋217呎單位　以292萬易手","createTime":"2017-11-17T04:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:54:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"558f09ba07c768b41339274a6124ec3666e8f69f","tid":471211,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"11月16日(四) 21:51   <br />\n<br />\n公屋自由市場亦錄創高價成交。中原梁岳宏表示，青衣長發邨敬發樓中層04室，實用面積約217方呎，獲買家以292.8萬元購入，實用呎價約13,493元，創同區同類物業新高。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171116/mobile/bkn-20171116215107899-1116_00842_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171116%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171116215107899-1116_00842_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=BMeVM3TIdM2uoKT7xN9I%2B8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2c435d22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171116/mobile/bkn-20171116215107899-1116_00842_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"065ac18607d3da1c242d2d251ac618d81daa830d","tid":471211,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b536f9513606eced8f7e97d13d66395e438e15","tid":471211,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"292萬， 我樓下南位都買唔到啦"},{"pid":"699cdf8e2321154524f32a95e8c2029653d89a41","tid":471211,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>292萬， 我樓下車位都買唔到啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f1eb283e42b20f3f6f31ed1ce44c10b3d03c590","tid":471211,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}